
         [ REST API / Controller ]
                     │
                     ▼
        (Creates ReserveCourseCommand)
                     │
                     ▼
        [ Kafka Producer → Topic: course-reservation-commands ]
                     │
                     ▼
        [ Kafka Consumer (CourseReservationService) ]
                     │
         Executes Command via Handler
                     │
                     ▼
        [ Kafka Producer → Topic: course-reservation-events ]
                     │
                     ▼
        [ Kafka Sink Connector ]
                     │
                     ▼
           Inserts into Database (course_reservations)

[Controller]
    ↓
[StudentService]
    ↓
[CourseReservationCommandProducer] → topic: course-reservation-commands
    ↓
[CommandListener] → executes ReserveCourseCommand
    ↓
[CourseReservationService.reserveCourse()]
    ↓
[CourseReservationEvent] created
    ↓
Publish → topic: course-reservation-events
    ↓
[Kafka Connect Sink Connector]
    ↓
[PostgreSQL] course_reservation_events table



